• I’ve identified the key reason your exact logo example looks seamless: those characters are in U+2580..U+259F
  (Block Elements), and mintty routes that range to a self-drawn renderer, not ordinary font fallback. I’ll grab the
  final confirming snippets and summarize the mechanism clearly.

